activate GM

GM --> GC: Return processed graph data
deactivate GM

GC -> Sigma: Render graph
activate Sigma

Sigma -> UI: Display graph visualization
deactivate Sigma

UI -> GC: Request graph manipulation
activate GC

GC -> GM: Update graph model
activate GM

GM --> GC: Return updated graph data
deactivate GM

GC -> Sigma: Update graph visualization
activate Sigma

Sigma -> UI: Display updated graph
deactivate Sigma

User -> UI: Request pathfinding
activate UI

UI -> PE: Execute A* algorithm
activate PE

PE --> UI: Return pathfinding results
deactivate PE

